<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.1.1">
<l>vāyun tiraiyukaḷuṅ kāṉaṉ maṭanārā</l>
<l>yāyu mamarulakun tuñcilunī tuñcāyāṉ</l>
<l>nōyum payalaimaiyu mītūra vemmēpōṉ</l>
<l>nīyun tirumālā ṉeñcaṅkōṭ paṭṭāyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Youthful herons of the seashore grove that leap the successive waves,</l>
<l>even when mother and the tranquil world sleep you do not sleep.</l>
<l>While pain and pallor press hard, like us,</l>
<l>are you too caught at the heart by Tirumāl?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
